Name: Olympus DAO
Tagline: Decentralized financial reserve protocol providing sustainable compounding interest
Mission: Our mission is to onboard the masses to a welcoming digital financial system. Velocity of currency creates an economy; the more capital flowing through our econOHMy the more it will grow. Unsurprisingly, the approach here is the same we’ve always had — if we build it, they will come.
Values: Inclusivity: To build an inclusive community, to welcome those outside the Olympus ecosystem equally.
